title Async Receive Data

actor User
participant "Subscription<T, R>" as Subscription
participant "SampleContainer<Sample<T>>" as SampleContainer
participant "Sample<T>" as Sample

User -> SampleContainer: new(capacity)
SampleContainer --> User: Empty SampleContainer

User -> Subscription: receive(\n  sample_container,\n  min_samples,\n  max_samples\n).await
Note over Subscription: Async waits until\nmin_samples are available
Subscription --> User: (SampleContainer, Result<usize>)

alt Samples Received (Ok(n))
    Note over User: n samples added to container

    User -> SampleContainer: pop_front()
    SampleContainer --> User: Option<Sample<T>>

    alt Sample is Some
        User -> Sample: Deref (*sample)
        Sample --> User: &T immutable reference

        User -> User: Access event data fields
        Note over User: Read-only access
    end

else Error
    Note over User: Handle error,\ncontainer still returned
end

@enduml
